{"tid":267604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求救-學生資助處","createTime":"2017-06-02T11:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T05:33:30.000Z","uid":118143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89a57d410d94c0461e71b5e69d79b7a41200b104","tid":267604,"uid":118143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T11:44:31.000Z","msg":"今年final year俾學生資助處抽中要重新審查銀行<br />\n但老爸老媽可能有個户口太耐漏報上去<br />\n一收到要審查已經交翻文件同銀行資料<br />\n但個筆錢係佢地儲定退休用<br />\n加上我今年學費6萬8淨claim得1萬多又左查右查<br />\n我已經好攰，填好多好多份文件俾佢follow同查<br />\n兩個月前又要簽翻份聲明<br />\n今日又打俾老爸老媽，但佢地翻工吵missed call<br />\n就打俾我去揾佢地，今次唔知又咩事<br />\n想請問大家漏報户口是不是要上法庭？還咗錢都要？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n超頹，本身已經唔多錢用，又查呢樣個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  Sorry 1999"},{"pid":"a8b161dd284d5d8e78fa774c75cd5754b8086cb0","tid":267604,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T11:47:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afc8a052c0360283df6e11a43748ef98801b9f97","tid":267604,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c1c2cd2d02aa1c85fc9268cffa73439a9123138","tid":267604,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"屌你 無端端有一頗想點 我成家養埋你"},{"pid":"1c976de11782796294c4fc2aea682e062e555299","tid":267604,"uid":113610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T11:52:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8948aec2f377e1f146da3638d7df94bc5e900d91","tid":267604,"uid":183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T11:52:35.000Z","msg":"之前d新聞還返錢就無事 好似係"},{"pid":"29376deea162a005a30da4fd0be47887be5f3269","tid":267604,"uid":5725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"